title: Build A Disney Princess And We'll Guess Your Age And Dream Job
text:
Build A Disney Princess And We’ll Guess Your Age And Dream Job You got: 14 years old and pop star 
You’re talented, ambitious, and driven to make your mark on the world. You love being the centre of attention and crave fame and fortune. You got: 18 years old and politician 
You’re smart, driven, and a natural-born leader. You want to make the world a better place and dream of being in charge and making a difference. You got: 22 years old and writer 
You’re creative and a bit of a daydreamer. You love reading and are full of your own stories you want to share with the world. You got: 24 years old and veterinarian 
You’re caring and compassionate. You adore animals and want to dedicate your life to helping them. You got: 28 years old and firefighter 
You’re fierce and brave. You care deeply about helping others and would put your life on the line to save someone else. You got: 32 years old and teacher 
You’re intelligent and obsessed with learning. You want to pass that passion on and inspire a whole new generation to be great. You got: 37 years old and reality tv star 
You’re fun-loving and outgoing. You love being the centre of attention and feel like you have a lot to give to the world just by being yourself. You got: 44 years old and astronaut 
You dream big and never give up. You’re fascinated by the universe and the mysteries of life, and would love to actually touch the stars. SHARE YOUR RESULTS
